HEADWORD: Aztec
<hw>Az"tec</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or relating to one
of the early races in Mexico that inhabited the great plateau of that
country at the time of the Spanish conquest in 1519.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the Aztec race or
people.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

